Korálky Katlas zaznamenaly zvýšený výskyt podvodné a zdraví škodlivé bižuterie na trhu v době ekonomické krize, kdy lidé více šetří. Zákazníci hlásí problémy a podvody s bižuterií jak v České republice, tak v zahraničí.

knowledgePieces.name: untitled

knowledgePieces.content: Korálky Katlas připravily shrnutí důležitých bodů, na které by si zákazníci měli dávat pozor při nákupu hotové bižuterie i bižuterních polotovarů. Tyto informace byly prezentovány během online setkání.

knowledgePieces.title: Creative Marketplace: Korálky Katlas VIP
knowledgePieces.content:
---

Korálky Katlas offers a VIP space in their store where creative sellers can rent shelves to display and sell their products through commission sales.

knowledgePieces.name: shelf-adoption-simple-steps-explained
knowledgePieces.title: Shelf Adoption: Simple Steps Explained
knowledgePieces.content: To adopt a shelf, fill out a form at the bottom of the article specifying the desired shelf, quantity, and rental period. The company will then contact you to finalize details.

knowledgePieces.name: storage-rental-pricing-and-discounts
knowledgePieces.title: Storage Rental Pricing and Discounts
knowledgePieces.content: Current shelf pricing for 2024 is available through a provided link. Discounts are offered for longer rental periods: 7% for 3-5 months, 15% for 6-11 months, and 30% for 12 or more months.

knowledgePieces.name: retail-partnership-agreement-documents
knowledgePieces.title: Retail Partnership Agreement Documents
knowledgePieces.content: Downloadable documents include a shelf rental agreement, commission sales agreement, and a protocol for transferring goods for commission sales.

knowledgePieces.name: shelf-occupancy-status-table
knowledgePieces.title: Shelf Occupancy Status Table
knowledgePieces.content: A table showing the current occupancy of individual shelves is available.
